cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on semantic segmentation of panoramic images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of synthetic data and experiments with different field of view (FoV) also suggest a machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) focus. The stitching of images and creation of a new dataset could also be considered graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM) related.
